  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8069005/" class="title-link">青铜骑士</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8069005"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/150507611/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/150507611/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">灵魂的荷尔蒙吨</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-09-01"
      class="main-meta">2016-09-01 22:08:23</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8069005_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  欧根是《青铜骑士》中的唯一出场的人物，自然是当之无愧的主角。”在某一处任职，一个要人也不认识，既不向往死去的祖先，也没有叹息已逝的流年“，通过这些描写，诗人向我们塑造了一个出身卑微，贫寒忧郁的社会底层人物形象。

